4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge in the field. Over a span of 16 weeks, students will participate in three live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. The curriculum focuses on foundational skills in Windows and Linux server administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Additionally, students will learn risk management and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, participants receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop